msgctxt "84_Saejima"
msgid "You're getting in the way, standin' there like that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "96_Angry Homeless Man"
msgid "You won't believe this! I found 1,000 yen on the ground\\r\n"
"in the <Color:7>underground mall<Color:Default>－a whole thousand!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "108_Saejima"
msgid "Wow. That's damn near a fortune."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "120_Angry Homeless Man"
msgid "I know, right? But then suddenly, while I wasn't looking, this little shit came up and the money was gone!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "132_Saejima"
msgid "You lost your cash takin' a shit?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "144_Angry Homeless Man"
msgid "No, I mean a pint-sized pickpocket at the <Color:7>underground mall<Color:Default>."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "156_Angry Homeless Man"
msgid "There I was, freaking about what I'd do if anyone tried\\r\n"
"to mug me, when a child ran up and snatched it away!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "168_Angry Homeless Man"
msgid "You're fast, right? Then go on, catch that thief for me!\\r\n"
"Catch him and teach him a lesson!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "180_Saejima"
msgid "Gotta say, the only lesson that needs learnin' here\\r\n"
"is for you to hold onto your shit better. Let it go."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "192_Angry Homeless Man"
msgid "Wow, that's just cold. I hope he goes after you next."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "204_Saejima"
msgid "(A little kid's pickin' pockets in the <Color:7>underground mall<Color:Default>? Sounds like a shitstorm waiting to happen. Ah, well.)"
msgstr ""

